       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PAYCALC.
       AUTHOR. JANE DOE.
      * COMPUTES THE MONTHLY SERVICE FEE: 250 BASIS POINTS OVER PRIME.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-FEE-RATE         PIC 9(2)V99 VALUE 2.50.
       01  WS-CUSTOMER-NAME    PIC X(30)  VALUE 'ACME HOLDINGS'.
       01  WS-BALANCE          PIC S9(7)V99 COMP-3.
       01  WS-TIER-TABLE.
           05  WS-TIER OCCURS 5 TIMES PIC 9(3).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-PARA.
           MOVE 1250.75 TO WS-BALANCE
           COMPUTE WS-BALANCE = WS-BALANCE * WS-FEE-RATE / 100
           IF WS-CUSTOMER-NAME = 'ACME HOLDINGS'
              DISPLAY 'VIP CLIENT: ' WS-CUSTOMER-NAME
           END-IF
           PERFORM FEE-PARA 3 TIMES
           GOBACK.
       FEE-PARA.
           ADD 10 TO WS-BALANCE.
